title: Trade, Fed & Mueller
itunes:title: Trade, Fed & Mueller
description:
Kevin spoke with Mattie Duppler, Senior Fellow at the National Taxpayers Union and former Former Coalitions Director for the House Republican Conference, and Marc Ross, founder of Caracal Global. They discussed Trump trade talks, Mueller, and the Federal Reserve policy decision.
